<plot>Fallen Apple explores the story of Specialist Adam Hawkins, a member of the military police at the infamous Abu Ghraib. Hawkins visits a psychologist to recall, in vivid flashback, the horrors of living and working in the military prison. Hawkins becomes embroiled in a worldwide scandal over the alleged torture tactics. When the soldier claims that he is unfairly being targeted by his superiors, Dr. Leigh takes it upon herself to discover the truth. Is Hawkins a victim of a larger conspiracy? Or is he just one of a few sadistic bad apples?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?188222</url></doc>
